  "texts": [
    "To reduce the injection of poisonous contents inside the network, the NKBF is used to forward the interests to trusted content sources.",
    "If there is still some poison content between consumer and content sources, the MFBIP performs on-demand signature verification and reissues an interest for the desired content.",
    "MFBIP eliminates poisoned content from CS as soon as possible and carries valid data to the clients.",
    "Moreover, it restores valid content for future interests without requiring any out-of-band communications.",
    "The propose scheme consists of three phases;"
